data.description: Surprisingly spacious single-floor living with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Bonus feature: the existing VA loan with a LOW interest rate may be assumable by a qualified buyer.  Move in just in time to take advantage of the warm heat generated by the pellet stove.  Solar panels have been installed to reduce your energy costs. No need to worry about a power outage! There's an outdoor generator plug to connect a generator of your choice. Some big-ticket upgrades have already been completed: kitchen, bathroom off primary bedroom, window replacements (with the exception of the window from the kitchen to the breezeway), and roof is 10-11 years of age.  The attached garage can double as a workshop with added overhead lighting.
